OL,3,CFarmer convicted after allowing his
OL,4,Cgrandchild to illegally ride in his
OL,5,Ctractor
OL,7,FVideo footage captured by a neighbour
OL,8,Fshowed the moment a farmer allowed one
OL,9,Fof his grandchildren to illegally ride
OL,10,Fin his tractor that led to his
OL,11,Fconviction.
OL,13,FHoward Walters, 78, from Swansea was
OL,14,Fgiven a one year community order after
OL,15,Fhe was seen with the child in the
OL,16,Ftractor cab on his farm in Swansea.
OL,18,FWalters had already been issued with a
OL,19,Fprohibition notice by the Health and
OL,20,FSafety Executive (HSE) in November
OL,21,F2020.
