OL,3,CFarmer convicted after allowing his
OL,4,Cgrandchild to illegally ride in his
OL,5,Ctractor
OL,7,FHe admitted to inspectors that he
OL,8,Fallowed his pre-teen grandchild to
OL,9,Fride in his tractor.
OL,11,FBut just two months later, he was
OL,12,Ffilmed by his neighbour flagrantly
OL,13,Fbreaching the terms of that notice.
OL,15,FA HSE inspector who investigated Mr
OL,16,FWalters said the law is "very clear".
OL,18,FChildren under 13 are specifically
OL,19,Fprohibited from driving or riding on
OL,20,For in any agricultural machine,
OL,21,Fincluding the tractor cab.
