OL,4,Cgrandchild to illegally ride in his
OL,5,Ctractor
OL,7,FAt the time of committing the offence,
OL,8,FWalters, of Tirmynydd Farm in
OL,9,FBirchgrove was already the subject of
OL,10,Fa suspended prison sentence for
OL,11,Funrelated environmental offences.
OL,13,FIn a case that was heard on 27 August
OL,14,F2024 at Swansea Crown Court, he was
OL,15,Ffined #500 for breaching the terms of
OL,16,Fthat sentence.
OL,18,FAs part of his community order,
OL,19,FWalters must attend 25 days of
OL,20,Frehabilitation.
