OL,3,CFarmer convicted after allowing his
OL,4,Cgrandchild to illegally ride in his
OL,5,Ctractor
OL,7,FHoward Walters pleaded guilty and was
OL,8,Fgiven a 12 month community order and
OL,9,Fordered to pay #3,000 in costs.
OL,11,FHSE inspector Simon Breen said: "The
OL,12,Flaw around children being allowed in
OL,13,Fthe cabs of any agricultural vehicle
OL,14,Fis very clear. For any child to ride
OL,15,Fon agricultural machinery like a
OL,16,Ftractor is unsafe and illegal.
OL,18,F"The fact this farmer chose to ignore
OL,19,Fa prohibition notice for putting his
OL,20,Fgrandchildren at risk is all the more
OL,21,Fstaggering.
